"""Server/network/NFS configuration planning for aerolitctl.

This module is the safe "configure" side of the old network helper,
setup_nfs_bundle.sh, and bootstrap controller NFS/group-vars generation logic.

It does not apply system changes. It does not run nmcli, firewall-cmd,
